items.title: Machine Learning with Ruby
items.content_text:
### Machine Learning Libraries / Vector search

*   [flann (⭐2.3k)](https://github.com/mariusmuja/flann) -
    Ruby bindings for the [FLANN (⭐2.3k)](https://github.com/flann-lib/flann) (Fast Library for Approximate Nearest Neighbors). <sup>\[[flann](#flann)]</sup>
*   [annoy-rb (⭐36)](https://github.com/yoshoku/annoy.rb) -
    Ruby bindings for the [Annoy (⭐14k)](https://github.com/spotify/annoy) (Approximate Nearest Neighbors Oh Yeah).
*   [hnswlib.rb (⭐15)](https://github.com/yoshoku/hnswlib.rb) -
    Ruby bindings for the [Hnswlib (⭐4.8k)](https://github.com/nmslib/hnswlib) that implements approximate nearest neighbor search with Hierarchical Navigable Small World graphs.
*   [ngt-ruby (⭐53)](https://github.com/ankane/ngt-ruby) -
    Ruby bindings for the [NGT (⭐1.3k)](https://github.com/yahoojapan/NGT) (Neighborhood Graph and Tree for Indexing High-dimensional data).
items.content_html:
Machine Learning Libraries / Vector search

  • flann (⭐2.3k) - Ruby bindings for the FLANN (⭐2.3k) (Fast Library for Approximate Nearest Neighbors). [flann]
  • annoy-rb (⭐36) - Ruby bindings for the Annoy (⭐14k) (Approximate Nearest Neighbors Oh Yeah).
  • hnswlib.rb (⭐15) - Ruby bindings for the Hnswlib (⭐4.8k) that implements approximate nearest neighbor search with Hierarchical Navigable Small World graphs.
  • ngt-ruby (⭐53) - Ruby bindings for the NGT (⭐1.3k) (Neighborhood Graph and Tree for Indexing High-dimensional data).
